A: I'm not sure what you mean by "clean disconnect".  If you want to kill the process, you can use the following code:
channel.sendSignal("KILL");

If you want to close the channel, you can use the following code:
channel.disconnect();

If you want to close the session, you can use the following code:
session.disconnect();
